      "date": "2012-01-25 06:51:17.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Fails\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 5.7/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/dd552e84-4709-11e1-a8d9-5254004bbbd3).  Ran 21 tests.  2 tests failed: obdfilter-survey, ost-pools.",
